modules.description: This module provides numerical solvers for initial value problems of ordinary differential equations, including LSODA and LSODAR algorithms. It supports dense and banded Jacobians, automatic stiffness detection, and root-finding capabilities for systems with sign-changing constraints. The module operates on vector and matrix types represented via Bigarray for efficient numerical computations, and is suitable for applications like physics simulations, chemical kinetics, and engineering systems modeling.
